        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'The manuscript is not fraudulent. The calculations are precise. My own formulas confirm the frame possesses overclock potential beyond standard parameters. But there\\'s one condition: fill up that \"defective\" black box.', 4: '13'}"
    },
    {
