        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'Hah? What kind of idea is that now? Multiple M.I.N.D.s in one frame? Even if they didn\\'t tear each other apart, the consciousness rejection would shred the frame. You\\'d be building a chimera.', 4: '1'}"
